{"tid":572851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咖啡仔我屌你老母，祝你班仆街冚家剷","createTime":"2018-02-26T02:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T04:00:45.000Z","uid":58104,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d654384808961c4ffaedc78acd01d87e381d7e","tid":572851,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩碧街落車行過見到幾個咖啡仔乜撚野交通督導員，我當場嚇一跳，然後得啖笑。呢個鐘數等成個紅燈車都無架捉人亂過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪撚同我講乜撚野亂過馬路犯法，隔離通菜街，花園街咁撚多紅van亂泊車唔撚過去督導下，屌你老母選擇性執法，欺善怕惡。<br />\n<br />\n利申，一早見到幾個咖啡仔無中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c772ff3950c6659787b7f2aa727359fffe4a9a","tid":572851,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"第一眼見到咖哩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a561ce0654582cd8dc631b08b21dc7f63c06c2","tid":572851,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13c772ff3950c6659787b7f2aa727359fffe4a9a","tid":572851,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"第一眼見到咖哩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"我都係每邊馬路派兩個 一個十字路口成十個咖啡仔，見唔到都幾on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebd2c9f5eb6f49a8e7d59ba5bd0736fc5c5b464","tid":572851,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a561ce0654582cd8dc631b08b21dc7f63c06c2","tid":572851,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13c772ff3950c6659787b7f2aa727359fffe4a9a","tid":572851,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci